Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家这么晚还在外面游荡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  必须得惩罚一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使不是已经不会伤害我们了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是不会对毫无抵抗的我们进行攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游离子  我们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  以半圆形围住她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你这家伙在发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被distortion挡开  也不要停下攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:25.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快闪开  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么深的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是致命伤也会很快好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的家伙居然有两个  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界什么时候变得这么莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有缘由的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得天使领域入侵作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的电脑里不是有一个开发技能的软件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里面有几个从未见过的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是其中一个叫「harmonics」的技能发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个什么样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时没看画面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把一个身体分裂成两个的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这也是天使自己用软件开发的技能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉并非是完全相同的两个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这家伙不同  很好战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她只使用保护自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀刃时也一样  只是为了挡住子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们这群废物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  音无同学除外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为笨蛋基本都聚集在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉你们其中一个可能性好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设那个分身的产生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在拥有强烈的攻击意志的时候的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说分身一直遵从着当时本体的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  奏不可能拥有强烈的攻击意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这无所谓  不过你好像很护着她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  她很可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在的问题是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天使的分身战斗的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是消除方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.27,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙在干什么  快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果分身是因为她的意志而产生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也应该能用她的意志来消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要等她醒来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果能用意志消除的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她还会躺在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是无意识下的产物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以连她也无法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同归于尽也只好拼命上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不会消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂不是要一直在这个世界存在下去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在放过了我们  但明天开始应该不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦偏离规范行为  恐怕会立刻和昨天一样变成一场血战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  因为她完全继承了约束我们的那份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上生性好战  糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想反抗也没有时间去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些时间要怎样去争取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上课  并装作听课的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能去听老师讲课的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真上课的话就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被分身发现的情况下干别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且坚持一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望下次再见的时候  不要少了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使领域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我知道可以分身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没办法让另一个消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel  Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软件的使用手册吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这么厚一本还全是英语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就没什么时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是距离吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是连上这个指令就会自动消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它的发动条件是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆把整个电脑都破坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴吗  那分身就不会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  直接改写成我能明白的程序算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间限制是10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒钟要等起来还真是漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不能设置到10秒以下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分身做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要删除掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  都做得这么周密了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽可能少修改一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要她再使用一次「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「absorb」这个技能就会发动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就会回到本体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏和我约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会和我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做过那种约定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副凌乱的样子肯定是被绑走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改写了程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她再使用一次那个力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加能力就会发动  分身就应该会回到本体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临阵磨枪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敌人的行动比预想的还快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被藏起来的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要一边躲避凶恶的天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是假装上课就已经够麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻到底能撑多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻是说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是为了什么加入GDM的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为崇拜岩泽同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM可是为了佯攻而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  面对那么可怕的对手怎么佯攻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你佯攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里我可是你的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么反倒是你发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈吗  真是对不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  虽然在演唱会中可能会尿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会退缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份决心先谢谢你了  不过现在还不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集目击到天使的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  yo!  Check  this  out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moonwalk, it's a moonwalk... Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚收集来的情报看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁的场所很可能是在Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  一定是在那最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个爆破掉的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  陷阱也还开启着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最为危险  距离这里最远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要潜入这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次可几乎是全灭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一个死的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家我即使尿裤子也会继续唱下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现出自己的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对那种对手  佯攻也是等着被秒杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不需要佯攻  堂堂正正地去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要兼顾和天使的战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战内容是空降至Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其最底层顺利夺回天使的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.88,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的陷阱搁着没人管  真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…在这里碰上天使的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是会尿裤子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请有所谓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请有所谓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有手枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由射击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会比预想的更快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是敌人又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  那家伙又是第一个被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后的要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想这个的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先对付眼前的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游离子  快没子弹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去封住路口  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能赶上的人就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么凶暴的天使居然有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次空降作战的处境还要糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会出现第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身都使出「handsonic」和「distortion」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说「harmonics」也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是一群低能儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  音无同学除外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来总结问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是究竟制造了多少个分身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分身能制造分身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那数量就没有限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那别说是两个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十个…二十个  说不定还有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由理已经追加过技能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身是会回到本体的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等她们消失不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是第二个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那能力追加以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就已经量产了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民们  终于注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  音无同学是高贵的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道我们会潜入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把已经量产了的分身布置在这个Guild的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后已经有两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聚集了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说被困在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连武器也没法补给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是等着被干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这种事到底有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就结果而言是让我们完全服从吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们老老实实地消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个把我们一网打尽的绝妙作战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.95,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…浪费子弹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  趁我还有意识的时候快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这种好像只有在临死时才是条好汉的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  趁现在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住啊  松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让松下君白白牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前进那是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天使身体比较小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要封住她的动作的话  那样做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天使有多么大的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的固技对她都会有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下君教我们的柔道终于有实用的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说对付一个天使只要牺牲一个人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后只要我们能救出本体  他们也都能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.41,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B12
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  my  turn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get  chance  and  luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么啊  这种像少年漫画最终回一样的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了  继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现这身肌肉的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去意识到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一名小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  在那片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个神情很寂寞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来让你露出笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是坏透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无同学  不是的  请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是善意的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  谁来说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我连他名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.90,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild联络通道  B15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第几个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  早就没在数了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的话就给我快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜欢他还是讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild被爆破后的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.20,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild最底层  爆炸中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里能一口气下到最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无君和由依去找本体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到  就催促她使用「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向君不是也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她等着的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了  根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请提一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这如果是最后一次作战就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由依呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只听到一声很短暂的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了天使的牺牲品了吗  太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是马上就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次活下来的又只有我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该是最后一个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你别在这里发呆了  快点去找本体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有晕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞着耳塞听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  就用另一把匕首割破你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战线的大家都拼上了性命来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点勉强你很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望你能使用一个能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你用了大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体能受得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只用一次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像改写了程序啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  一切都会回到她的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多冷酷的我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是分身也有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击你们的众多的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到她的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性吸收这么多的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得会没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏


